result.notes:
Ten annual surveys in a series of Fisheries Science Partnership (FSP) surveys 
of cod, haddock and whiting in the Irish Sea that commenced in spring 2004, 
and evaluates the time-series of data on catch rates, distribution and age 
composition in the western (commercial whitefish otter trawler) and eastern 
Irish Sea (midwater (semi-pelagic) trawler).
